snippet.title: CASE: Animatronics – Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/489360/

Control of the police department is in the hands of anonymous hacker. All exits are locked. Electricity is off. Metallic thumps are getting closer. Will you survive, Detective Bishop?
